metadata.name: Casanakas #1
metadata.description:
Casanakas para Nakamigos! 

1/1 Unique and personalized houses resembling Nakamigos that you own, built at your request by Alley Tac. Check my Twitter/pinned tweet to find out how to order your own. All art CC0. 

Enjoy your Casanakas! Home parties allowed all over the metaverse.
